## RECIPE BOOK -------------------------

### Get all recipe books (public + owned by user + collaborator)
GET http://localhost:3000/recipe-books  
Authorization:  Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

### Create a new recipe book
POST http://localhost:3000/recipe-books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization:  Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

{
  "name": "My chocolate Recipe Book 1",
  "description": "A collection of my favorite recipes.",
  "isPublic": false
}

### Add a recipe to a recipe book 
POST http://localhost:3000/recipe-books/69a99a31aacff322e1ab6630/recipes/69a99a0caacff322e1ab662a
Authorization: Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

### Delete a recipe from a recipe book
DELETE http://localhost:3000/recipe-books/69a99a31aacff322e1ab6630/recipes/69a93311162ec36c1122f577
Authorization: Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

### Get my recipe books (owned by user)
GET http://localhost:3000/recipe-books/my
Authorization: Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

### Get a recipe book by ID (owner or collaborator)
GET http://localhost:3000/recipe-books/69a92e150084ffb2c89b62d2
Authorization: Bearer "PASTE_TOKEN_HERE"

### Update a recipe book
